Package de.uka.ipd.sdq.simucom.rerunsimulation.runconfig

Contains the runconfig of the rerun simulation.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GeneratedProjectChooseSimulationTab
    The tab in the rerun simulation configuration that shows the generated project and its models used.
    RerunSimuComConfigurationTab
    This tab is basically the same tab as SimuComConfigurationTab.
    RerunSimuComWorkflowConfiguration
    Configuration class for the rerun simulation plug-in.
    RerunSimuComWorkflowLauncher
    Starts the RerunSimulaionWorkflowLauncher instead of the workflow launcher that is started in the superclass
    RerunSimulationTabGroup
    The tab group for the rerun simulation
    RerunSimulationWorkflowLauncher
    This class creates the RerunSimulationJob which is needed for rerunning the simulation without having to delete the original data

Package de.uka.ipd.sdq.simucom.rerunsimulation.runconfig Description

Contains the runconfig of the rerun simulation. The runconfig contains classes such as the launch configuration tab group needed or the workflow launcher that redirects to the jobs package to execute all the jobs.
Author:
Michael Junker
